document_data.mainbody:
Gathgaer Milomynts residence was a row house and the home of Gathgaer Milomynt located in Waterdeep during the mid-to-late 14 century DR.
The home stood two stories tall.
Gathgaer Milomynts residence was located in the north section of Waterdeeps Dock Ward on the east side of Drawn Sword Alley.
